- Ada banyak masalah

1012
00:54:33,310 --> 00:54:36,149
selama proses syuting dokumenter Oh Hyuk.

1013
00:54:36,509 --> 00:54:38,350
Ajarilah sutradara kami

1014
00:54:38,680 --> 00:54:41,919
